headline: Carrier Recognized for Advancing Inventory Management through Digital Supply Chain Transformation
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, has been named a finalist in the Digital Supply Chain category of the 2025 Manufacturing Leadership Awards, presented by the National Association of Manufacturers' Manufacturing Leadership Council.

headline: Trane Technologies (TT) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Trane Technologies (TT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 11.36% and 5.13%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
